  "what_to_build": "One complete self-contained single-page website per lead in this manifest (20 leads). Each site is ONE file named <slug>.html with ALL CSS and JS inline. No external fonts, scripts, or stylesheets. These are trial websites for small local trade businesses in Yorkshire, England.",
  "hero_logo_CRITICAL": "For each lead, fetch the plain-text file at logo_datauri_url. Its entire content is a single line starting with 'data:image/png;base64,'. Paste that whole string as the src of an <img> at the top of the hero section: <img class='hlogo' src='<the string>' alt='<business> logo'>. Style .hlogo { max-width: min(320px, 70vw); height: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto 1rem; }. Do NOT skip this. Do NOT try to fetch ad_image_url (you cannot fetch binary images) \u2014 the datauri text file IS the logo.",
  "design": "Design each site from its palette[] colours and ad_text. Use palette[0] as the primary brand colour. Clean, modern, mobile-first, professional. Sections: hero (logo, business name, one-line pitch, phone call-to-action button with tel: link), services (from ad_text), why-choose-us / trust points (experience, insured, free quotes \u2014 only claims present in ad_text), service area (town + surrounding area), contact section.",
  "contact_form": "Every site gets a contact form posting to https://formspree.io/f/mpqgeoaj with method POST, fields: name, phone, message, and a hidden input name='_subject' value='<business> enquiry'. Also show the business phone number prominently with a tel: link.",
  "phone_rule": "Use the exact phone (and landline if present) given in this manifest. Never invent phone numbers, emails, addresses, prices, or reviews.",
  "email_rule": "Only show an email address if the manifest email field is non-empty; use it exactly as written.",
  "footer": "Small footer: '<business> \u2014 <town>, <county>'. No fake copyright years, no invented company registration numbers.",
  "seo": "Each page: <title><business> | <category> in <town></title> and a meta description using the ad_text.",
  "deliverable": "Zip all 20 files as batch3.N-sites.zip (N = this manifest's number) and provide a download link or upload URL (litterbox.catbox.moe 72h, or any fetchable URL)."
 },
